      "name": "Wine Club How it Works",
      "settings": {
        "how_it_works_title": "How the Alvi’s Drift Private Club Works",
        "how_it_works_text": "<p><br/>    The Alvi’s Drift Private Club has three membership tiers: <strong>Bronze</strong>, <strong>Silver</strong>, and <strong>Gold</strong>.<br/>  <strong>Everyone starts on Bronze.</strong></p><p> As you shop in our online wine store, you earn points automatically, helping you move up<br/>    through the tiers and unlock greater rewards and exclusive savings.<br/>  </p><h4>How points work</h4><ul><li>Earn <strong>1 point</strong> for every <strong>R1</strong> spent in our online wine shop.</li><li>Points don’t expire and aren’t used to redeem products.</li><li>They simply track your membership level.</li><li>The more you shop, the higher your tier — and the more you save.</li><li>Tier discounts do not apply to sale or promotional wines.</li><li>Your discount is automatically applied at checkout.</li></ul>",
